description.narrative: The Samoa Tourism Growth Partnership (STGP) is a five-year programme of support which will in the first two years, support destination marketing (to the New Zealand market), product development, tourism trainings and tourism infrastructure. The final three years (2019/20-2022/23) are likely to focus on strengthening destination marketing, improving sector linkages, and further product and experience development.
